General.Description: TechTarget, Inc. provides purchase intent-driven marketing and sales data that delivers business impact for B2B companies. Its solutions are designed to enable B2B technology companies to identify, reach, and influence enterprise technology decision makers. It offers products and services intended to improve IT vendors' abilities to impact targeted audiences for business growth using targeting, first-party analytics and data services complemented with customized marketing programs that integrate content creation, demand generation, brand marketing, and other advertising techniques. The company is headquartered in Newton, Massachusetts. TechTarget, Inc operates as a subsidiary of Informa Us Holdings Limited.
